0. 数据库脚本准备，方便在任何地方搭建开发环境
   ==python 访问数据库==
   A. sudo apt-get install libmysqlclient-dev   
   B. https://pypi.python.org/pypi/MySQL-python/1.2.4#downloads 
   C. 解压 cd MySQL-python/1.2.4
   C. 修改 setup_proxy.py : mysql_config.path = "/usr/bin/mysql_config"
   D. python setup.py build ; python setup.py install
   E. 测试 cd com/changxia/access/db ; python MySqlHelper.py
   ==移库到公司的库中==
